Package: wikipediapreview
Title: Wikipedia Preview for R Markdown Documents
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mikhail", "Popov", email = "mikhail@wikimedia.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Wikimedia Inuka team", role = "ctb",
           comment = "Wikipedia Preview library"),
    person("Wikimedia Foundation", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Facilitates the use of 'Wikipedia Preview'
  <https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Wikipedia_Preview> in R Markdown documents and
  websites for showing a popup card with a short summary from Wikipedia when a
  reader hovers over a link to a Wikipedia article (on a desktop) or taps a link
  (on a mobile device).
URL: https://github.com/bearloga/wikipediapreview-r,
    https://bearloga.github.io/wikipediapreview-r/
BugReports: https://github.com/bearloga/wikipediapreview-r/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
